<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application' %>
</head>

<body style="background-color:#F9F9F9;padding-bottom:10px;padding-top:20px;">
  <div style="text-align:center;">
    <%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url, style:"height:26px; width:156px;" %>
    <div class="spacer" style="height:20px"></div>
  </div>

  <div style="padding:20px;margin-right:4%;margin-left:4%;background-color:#FFFFFF;">
    <h1 style="color:#0F78FF;">Transfer notification</h1>
    <div style="font-size:16px;line-height:150%;">
      <p>Just a heads up, we're about to transfer:</p>
       <p style="font-size:26px;font-weight:bold;text-align:center;">$<%=@amount%></p>
       <p style="text-align:center;">from <span style="font-weight:bold"><%=@source_institution%> - <%=@source%></span> to your <span style="font-weight:bold"><%=@deposit_institution%> - <%=@deposit%></span><br>on <span style="font-weight:bold"><%=@date%></span>.</p>
         <p>If you need to change or cancel the transfer you can do so from the app by backing out of the transactions.<br><br>Questions or issues? Contact us at feedback@noncents.co.</p>
        <p>Best,<br>noncents Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <%= image_tag attachments['divider.png'].url, style:"margin-left:4%;width:92%;margin-top:-25px;"%>
    <div style="text-align:center;padding-top:10px;">
      <p style="text-size:6px;color:#989EA6;line-height:150%;"><a href="http://noncents.co/">noncents</a><br>2660 South La Brea Ave • Los Angeles, CA • 90016</p>
    </div>

  </body>
  </html>
